title: Kubernetes: Storage Classes
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors a storage class of a kubernetes cluster.
 The check returns always returns {OK}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each storage class.

item:
 The name of the storage class.
